<h3 class="has-text-align-center">OUR SERVICES</h3>



<hr class="wp-block-separator is-style-wide"/>



<p>1. <strong>Feeding programs</strong> for strays (Dogs, cats, birds, pigeons, parrots, crows, cow, buffalo, donkeys etc.)</p>



<p>2. <b>Corporate employee engagement</b> activities such as:</p>



<ul><li>Team engagement activity to the place the mud pots for strays</li><li>Providing mud pots to place near by their home to feed strays</li><li>Volunteering programs where people can join us in their free time to feed strays</li><li>Donation drives where anyone can donate their food wastage which can be later collected by us to feed strays</li></ul>



<p class="has-text-align-left">3. <b>Awareness programs</b> on</p>



<ul><li>Increasing usage of eco-friendly mud pots for food and water for stray animals.</li><li>To place mud pots at safe places which are considered to be permanent feeding stations and awareness programs for people for the same.</li><li>To promote &amp; spread awareness among people for adoption instead of buying.</li><li>To develop animal health and welfare programs worldwide.</li><li>School, college &amp; corporate seminar activities to make the younger generation more aware of animal rights &amp; welfare.</li><li>To manage the food wastage at home, restaurants, offices etc. to feed stray animals.</li><li>To conduct volunteer programs to associate with more volunteers to spread information about animal love, medical care and feeding.</li><li><b>Campaigns</b><ol><li>PLACE A POT</li><li>SPAY/NEUTER PROGRAMS</li></ol></li></ul>



<p>4. <strong>About ongoing Feeding Drives</strong></p>



<ul><li>We are continuously conducting feeding drives on daily basis.</li></ul>



